response.overview: Mia Smiles returns and Paul Cox returns as well, this time meeting her in a hot, torrid, real unplanned scene! Jake returns and mixes it up with exotic Maya. Let`s stay with the M`s, when we meet Monti! Monte is our covergirl, and wow, Paul gets lucky again! His luck doesn`t run out when lovely Leah and him get it on and get it off! All in all this whole DVD is on! It`s in your hands, what are you waiting for? Get it! Love Ya, Ed Powers
